title: Skin Care & Everday Face Routine
description:
Hey guys!! So I had primer in my baby hairs!! Lol I hate when that happens, how embarrassing but hope you enjoyed anyway haaha

Products Used:
Loreal Magic Perfecting Base
Maybelline Instant age rewind erase dark sports concealer in light
Maybelline Fit me concealer in medium
Revive makeup blending applicator by beauty pro
Revlon Color stay pressed powder in light/medium
MAC mineralized skin finish in lightplus & give me sun
Wet & Wild blush in mellow wine
ELF translucent powder
Bonnebelle Lipgloss in cappuccino
The brushes used are from ELF & Sonia Kashuk which you can get at target

Like always thank you for watching! :)
xoxo,

Jasmine ♥
